name: magic mask character 1 kyoshi
description:
After 50 years when the demon lord was sealed, the human world was again peaceful.. A young man named kyoshi a happy go lucky, rascal and a problem for his father. Little did he know he was a descendant of a mask wielding family. After a unfortunate night happened he found out the secret about his family and the upcoming threat to the human world.
Kyoshi is one of the protagonist in the magic mask he owns the worn out mask that could summon elemental spirits however there are more secrets about the mask that he is weilding.
